# Environment Variables Template

## Local Development

Create a `.env.local` file in the root directory with:

```env
# Node Environment
NODE_ENV=development

# Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/reacher_dev

# Cache
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# Authentication
JWT_SECRET=dev-secret-key-change-in-production
JWT_EXPIRY=86400

# API
API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000
GATEWAY_PORT=5000
AUTH_SERVICE_PORT=5001
USER_SERVICE_PORT=5002
PRODUCT_SERVICE_PORT=5003
PROVIDER_SERVICE_PORT=5004
TRUST_SERVICE_PORT=5005
MESSAGE_SERVICE_PORT=5006
NOTIFICATION_SERVICE_PORT=5007

# Frontend
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=http://localhost:54321
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# Supabase (if using managed)
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_KEY=your-anon-key
SUPABASE_SECRET=your-secret-key

# Storage
STORAGE_BUCKET=reacher-uploads
STORAGE_TYPE=local

# Email (for notifications)
SMTP_HOST=localhost
SMTP_PORT=1025
SMTP_USER=test
SMTP_PASSWORD=test

# Logging
LOG_LEVEL=debug
```

## Production

Create a `.env` file with:

```env
NODE_ENV=production

DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@prod-db.amazonaws.com:5432/reacher
REDIS_URL=redis://user:password@upstash.io:6379

JWT_SECRET=your-strong-random-secret-key-min-32-chars
JWT_EXPIRY=86400

API_BASE_URL=https://api.reacher.app
GATEWAY_PORT=5000

NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.reacher.app
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-public-key

SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SECRET=your-secret-key

STORAGE_TYPE=s3
AWS_S3_BUCKET=reacher-prod
AWS_S3_REGION=us-east-1
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=your-access-key
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=your-secret-key

SMTP_HOST=smtp.sendgrid.net
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=apikey
SMTP_PASSWORD=SG.xxxxx

SENTRY_DSN=https://xxxxx@sentry.io/xxxxx

LOG_LEVEL=info
```

## Service-Specific Variables

### Auth Service
```env
PASSWORD_HASH_ROUNDS=10
REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRY=604800
```

### Notification Service
```env
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your-account-sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your-auth-token
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
```

### Message Service
```env
WEBSOCKET_ENABLED=true
MESSAGE_RETENTION_DAYS=90
```

---

**Never commit `.env` or `.env.local` files to version control.**
